## Docker Deployment

### Development
```bash
docker-compose up -d
# Access Jupyter: http://localhost:8888
```

### Production (Secure)
```bash
docker-compose -f docker/docker-compose.secure.yml up -d
# Includes: RabbitMQ, MQTT, Qdrant, Redis with TLS
```

